                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="question-two" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">To join a room in ToggleCord you must know the exact name of the room and it's password. Click the "Chat" button in your navigation and switch to join room. There fill the room details.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
